\v 1 Isabatha selidlulile\x + Mat. 28.1-8. Luka 24.1-10.\x*, uMariya Magadalena\x + 15.40.\x*\x + Joha. 20.1.\x* loMariya \add unina\add* kaJakobe\x + 15.40.\x* loSalome\x + 15.40.\x* bathenga amakha, ukuze bahambe bayemgcoba\x + Luka 23.56; 24.1. Joha. 19.40.\x*.
\v 2 Kwathi ekuseni kakhulu ngo\add suku\add* lokuqala lweviki beza engcwabeni\x + Luka 24.1. Joha. 20.1.\x*, ekuphumeni kwelanga\x + Mat. 13.6.\x*\x + Luka 24.1. Joha. 20.1.\x*.
\v 3 Basebekhulumisana \add besithi\add*: Ngubani ozasigiqela ilitshe lisuke emnyango wengcwaba?
\v 4 Futhi bathi ukukhangela babona ilitshe seligiqwe lasuswa; ngoba lalilikhulu kakhulu\x + 15.46.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Kuthe bengena engcwabeni\x + Mat. 28.2.\x*, babona ijaha lihlezi ngakwesokunene\x + Luka 24.3. Joha. 20.11,12.\x*, lembethe isembatho eside\x + 12.38. Luka 20.46.\x* esimhlophe\x + Isam. 6.11; 7.9,13.\x*; besaba\x + 9.15.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa lathi kubo: Lingesabi; lidinga uJesu umNazaretha obebethelwe; uvukile, kakho lapha; khangelani, indawo lapho abebembeke khona\x + 9.15.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa hambani, litshele abafundi bakhe loPetro ukuthi uzalandulela ukuya eGalili\x + 14.29,31,37,72.\x*; lizambona khona, njengalokho ayekutshilo kini\x + 14.28. Mat. 26.32.\x*.
