\v 20 Bona basebephuma batshumayela endaweni zonke, iNkosi isebenza la\add bo\x + 16.19. Heb. 2.3,4.\x*\add*, iqinisa\x + Heb. 2.3.\x* ilizwi\x + Luka 1.2.\x* ngezibonakaliso ezazilandela\x + Seb. 5.12; 14.3. Heb. 2.4.\x*. Ameni.
